[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ただいま、フリーゲン。\n何年経っても相変わらず、ほっとする田舎だね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00655",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "田舎には田舎の温かさがあるよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00656",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "変わらない毎日に退屈して、\n王都に憧れたんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00657",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "色々冒険して、戦って……変わらない場所も\nそれでいいところがあるなって思うようになったよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00658",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "イザナちゃん……ほんと、大きくなったわね。\nねぇ、今もハンマー好きなのは変わらず？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00659",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "今もハンマーこそがすべてだよ、メーヴェおばさん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00660",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "うぐっ！　おばさん呼びは効くわ……\n戦いで負った傷に響く……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00661",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "もう、お母さんたら。色々あったし、\nケガを治す間くらい、おうちでのんびりしようよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00662",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "やだやだ、お姉さんって呼ばれるまで\n私はここを動かないんだから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00663",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "相変わらずの自由奔放……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00664",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "アタシも早く帰って弟やパパに会いたいし……\nメーヴェお姉さん、許してください",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00665",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "うん、許したげる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00666",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "相変わらず立ち直りも早い……\nそうそう、イザナちゃんは騎士になったんだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00667",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "すごいじゃない！　夢を叶えたのね！\nもうすっかり私、追い越されちゃった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00668",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "追い越す？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00669",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "私、冒険者になる前は騎士になろうって思ってたのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00670",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そうなの？　知らなかった……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00671",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "実技は余裕だったんだけど、筆記で落ちちゃって。\nこりゃあもう私には無理だな～って",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00672",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "筆記試験、難しいもんね……アタシも\nハンマー勉強法を応用したりして……大変だったよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00673",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ちょっと最初の夢とは違ったけど、冒険者になって、\nそして冒険中に、あの人……ユリウスと出会ったの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00674",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "もう、めっちゃかっこよくって？\n何度も何度も言い寄って、やっと口説き落としたのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00675",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "メーヴェお姉さんから口説いたんだ！\nはわ……はわわ……はんまー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00676",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "お母さん力強いなぁ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00677",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ああ、ごめん。\nユリウスのことを思い出したら、つい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00678",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ううん、もっと聞きたいよ。\nお母さんとお父さんが仲良しで、娘として嬉しいもん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00679",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "お父さんが、まだ見つからないのは残念だけど、\nお母さんなら、きっと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00680",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00681",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "お母さん？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00682",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "……あ、ううん。こんな母親失格の私を\nお母さんって呼んでくれるんだなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00683",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ウェルテックスにやられて姿を消したユリウス。\nそれを追って、あなたを置いて旅に出た私……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00684",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ランターナ王国の外にも聞こえてきたあなたの名声。\n驚いたわ。嬉しかったし、申し訳なくも思った",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00685",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "イザナちゃんと同じで、とても立派に育ってくれた。\nユリウスが勝てなかった頂獣も倒してくれた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00686",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "……ありがとう。それと、ごめんね。\nあなたの世話をザスキアに任せきりにして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00687",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そのザスキアのことも聞いたけど……大丈夫？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00688",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん……私、自分で言うのもなんだけど、\n結構大人になれた気がする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00689",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "だからね。正直に教えてほしい。私……お母さんと\nお父さんから産まれた子じゃ、ないんだよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00690",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "え……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00691",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヘルトさんが言ってたよね、\n「偽りの血縁」って……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00692",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "なに言ってるの。私たちは家族よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00693",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00694",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "大丈夫。レスナちゃんにはアタシがついてる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00695",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "……あれは、私がユリウスと一緒に\n冒険をしていた時だったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00696",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "とある遺跡を探検していた時、声が聞こえた。\n赤ん坊の、泣き声が……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00697",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "泣き声は祭壇から聞こえてきた。\nなんでそこに赤ん坊がいるのか分からなかったけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00698",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "見過ごせないから、連れ帰って育てることにした。\nそれがあなた、レスナよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00699",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そっか……やっぱり……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00700",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レスナちゃん……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00701",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "…………う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00702",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ありがとう、私を拾って、育ててくれて。\n祭壇に置かれていたおかげだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00703",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 49,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "だから私はお母さんとお父さんと、\nイザナちゃんとだって出会えた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00704",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 50,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "レスナ……っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00705",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 51,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "……ごめんなさい、あなたがいつか\n大人になったら伝えようと思ってたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00706",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 52,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "そして、同時に伝えるのが怖かった。\nでも、あなたはもう立派に、大人だった……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00707",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 53,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "レスナ、私たちのところに来てくれて……\nこっちこそ、ありがとね……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00708",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 54,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん……うんっ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00709",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 55,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私にとって、血が繋がってなくても\n　お母さんは、お母さんだ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00710",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 56,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（でも、だとしたら……私を祭壇に置いたのは、\n　きっと――）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00711",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]